    "body": "Currently the RapidsBufferStore and subclasses define the spill cadance (who is my spill store) and they also rely on the catalog for unspill. This task is to completely remove the link store->catalog, enforcing a strict catalog->store flow.\r\n\r\nWe want to then make as much as possible private under the `com.nvidia.spark.rapids.spill` package. `RapidsBufferCatalog` has public methods that allow entry into this namespace.",
